lead_paragraph: Usain Bolt negotiated a series of delays and a false start in his own race before easily winning his quarter-final of the 100m in 10.15 seconds at Jamaica's national championships on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Bolt Staves Off False Starts to Move Into 100m Semi-Finals
headline.main: Bolt Staves Off False Starts to Move Into 100m Semi-Finals
